This plugin is an adaptation, not a verbatim copy: the nine separate Claude Code
plugins are unified into one protoAgent plugin, redundant skill variants are
consolidated, the skills are adapted to protoAgent's skill format, and the
PM Brain is re-implemented as protoAgent tools + a console view (rather than a
scaffolded directory of markdown). The frameworks, structure, and much of the
skill prose originate with Paweł Huryn; errors introduced in adaptation are ours.

